{"tid":1770860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教師再不是垃圾教畜：有超過五成教職員參與罷工，三成學校能正常上課","createTime":"2019-12-05T12:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T11:32:06.000Z","uid":174752,"like":347,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"91abb060b6d3b02144fbd0334dfb3314003eeeed","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>教育部長預料全國有超過五成教職員參與罷工，首都巴黎有七成多教師罷工；只有三成學校能正常上課</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n法國有示威者抗議政府改革退休制度，今日發起全國大罷工，法國國家鐵路公司估計，全國百分之90的高鐵列車將要停駛，停售今日至星期日共四日的列車車票。工國際鐵路交通亦將受嚴重影響，近半數歐洲之星列車的班次取消，鐵路公司已租用巴士取代運載量最大的鐵路線。<br />\n<br />\n不同行業都有從業員參與罷工，法國民航局表示，部分空管人員參與罷工，預計全國有兩成航班取消；教育部長預料全國有超過五成教職員參與罷工，首都巴黎有七成多教師罷工；只有三成學校能正常上課。<br />\n<br />\n發起示威的團體表示，遊行隊伍會從巴黎北站出發，途徑共和廣場抵達民族廣場，途徑的酒吧、餐館、商店都勒令關閉。巴黎將出動6000名警察和憲兵維持治安，香榭麗舍大道、愛麗舍宮、巴黎聖母院等區域將禁止黃背心進入<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496034-20191205.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496034-20191205.htm&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=d59556f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496034-20191205.htm&h=01987827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496034-20191205.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今次全港大團結，各行各業都為五大訴求罷工，罷市。<br />\n唯有香港教畜次次都雷聲大雨點小，由六月吹到依家成半年時間都未<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主動罷工</span></span>罷課過一次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我宣布香港教畜係垃圾，光環資源攞盡，係香港最低賤行業，與黑警，支共官員齊名。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9143b7afaf3dea78915018edde1f8c48b105d002","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"047b52be41526b06133898c6dc9949340e180e3f","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15b7dff0c6b0ff48b75d224c1dbd13bf8a7e9ecc","tid":1770860,"uid":45662,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"攞法國黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a0d63c1614b8dceae2ee1b2fe41dd36b2be035","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":18,"dislike":16,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我在此呼籲香港教畜回頭是岸，盡快組織一次大規模教師罷工。否則請香港人以後以教畜去稱呼香港所有教育工作者</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你班仆街教畜，連罷課都要菁菁學子都你哋做埋，成班成年人做到咁垃圾，羞唔羞恥？"},{"pid":"93c12619a252a1bf97b99e2ac1e3212fa4d0ad73","tid":1770860,"uid":160986,"like":72,"dislike":24,"score":48,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"就係你呢d仆街係到搞分化<br />\n迫走晒同路人<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"41201147623c393367c79db8941810840d6fac0c","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"15b7dff0c6b0ff48b75d224c1dbd13bf8a7e9ecc","tid":1770860,"uid":45662,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"攞法國黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"你要爭取民主，唔好用外國黎比呀，你要用北韓，支那黎比呀，on9仔"},{"pid":"89d5497e0f7a4fbe1c5c21f96537a34ffff10f59","tid":1770860,"uid":174752,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"93c12619a252a1bf97b99e2ac1e3212fa4d0ad73","tid":1770860,"uid":160986,"like":72,"dislike":24,"score":48,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"就係你呢d仆街係到搞分化<br />\n迫走晒同路人<br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"教畜你好"},{"pid":"5859337d8e9c40ccd0dc8614afa652fcb9820aa2","tid":1770860,"uid":204039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c12619a252a1bf97b99e2ac1e3212fa4d0